<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="165"><strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="165">Days</strong> – Enter the number of days in which the approval process must be completed. Then select the calendar that your organization uses, and enter information about your organization's work week.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="166"><strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="166">Weeks</strong> – Enter the number of weeks in which the approval process must be completed.</li>
