<h2 id="specify-which-actions-are-available-to-the-user" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="172">Specify which actions are available to the user</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="174">When a document is assigned to a user for approval, the user must act on the document. Follows these steps to specify which actions the user can take on the document that was submitted.</p>
<ol sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="176">
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="176">In the left pane, click <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="176">Advanced settings</strong>.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="177">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="177">Approve</strong> check box if the user can approve the document.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="178">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="178">Reject</strong> check box the user can reject the document.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="179">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="179">Request change</strong> check box the user can request changes to the document.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="180">Select the <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="180">Delegate</strong> check box if the user can assign the document to another user for approval.</li>
</ol>
<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="182">
