<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="183">The <strong sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="183">Enable actions from the work list in Enterprise Portal</strong> check box has been deprecated.</p>
