<h2 id="configure-the-approval-steps" sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="185">Configure the approval steps</h2>
<p sourcefile="articles/fin-ops-core/fin-ops/organization-administration/configure-approval-process-workflow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="187">An approval process consists of approval steps. Complete the following procedure to add steps the approval process and configure the steps.</p>
